frozen.name: cura-lulzbot
frozen.shortDescription: 3D printing host software for the Lulzbot
frozen.longDescription:
Cura LulzBot Edition is a fork of the 3D printing/slicing
software from Ultimaker, with changes to support 3D printers
from Aleph Objects.
